This decree outlines the administrative and operational requirements for all commercial mining operations within the designated Kuiper Belt Resource Zones.

> __article#CL7 2 compliance#CL9 environmental#CL9__
**Article 2: Environmental Compliance**
> __entity#CL10 all#CL10 participating#CL10 must#CL10 submit#CL10#FV assessment#CL10 comprehensive#CL10 CL10ASSOC impact#CL9 environmental#CL9 to#CL17 committee#CL5 CL5ASSOC oversight#CL9 ecological#CL9 CL5ASSOC confederation#CL9 solar#CL9 prior#CL16 to#CL17 deployment#CL9 CL9ASSOC vessel#CL10 CL10ASSOC extraction.#CL9__
All participating entities must submit comprehensive environmental impact assessments to the Solar Confederation Ecological Oversight Committee prior to the deployment of extraction vessels.

> __article#CL7 3 standard#CL10 CL10ASSOC labor#CL9__
**Article 3: Labor Standards**
> __confederation#CL9 guarantee#CL9#FV subsidy#CL10 standard#CL10 CL10ASSOC support#CL9 CL9ASSOC life#CL9 CONJ multiplier#CL10 CL10ASSOC pay#CL9 CL9ASSOC hazard#CL9 for#APPL personnel#CL9 all#CL9 deploy#CL9#PASS#PST to#CL17 habitat#CL10 orbital#CL10 CL10ASSOC Class#C CONJ lower.#CL10__
The Confederation guarantees standard life-support subsidies and hazard pay multipliers for all personnel deployed to Class-C orbital habitats or lower.

> __article#CL7 4 enforcement#CL9__
**Article 4: Enforcement**
> __fail#CL15#FV comply#INF#FV with#CL16 regulation#CL10 CL10DEM CL15FUT result#CL15#FV in#CL18 revocation#CL9 immediate#CL9 CL9ASSOC vector#CL10 CL10ASSOC transit#CL9 CONJ freeze#CL15#FV CL15ASSOC asset#CL7 all#CL7 associated#CL7 CL7ASSOC banking#CL9 central.#CL9__
Failure to comply with these regulations will result in the immediate revocation of transit vectors and the freezing of all associated central banking assets.
